ise-sur-les-reseaux-sociaux"> <article class="item type-normal abo"><div class="item-image"><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" data-srcset="https://www.courrierinternational.com/sites/ci_master/files/styles/image_235/public/illustrations/thumbnails/daech_reseaux_sociaux_0.jpg?itok=FG6XeqaU 380w, https://www.courrierinternational.com/sites/ci_master/files/styles/image_470/public/illustrations/thumbnails/daech_reseaux_sociaux_0.jpg?itok=1Ypv0CT_ 1024w" data-src="https://www.courrierinternational.com/sites/ci_master/files/styles/image_235/public/illustrations/thumbnails/daech_reseaux_sociaux_0.jpg?itok=FG6XeqaU" alt="Daech fragilisé sur les réseaux sociaux" sizes="(max-width:759px) 100vw, 50vw" class="lazyload"></div><div class="item-text"><h2 class="title"> <span class="strapline">Terrorisme.</span> Daech fragilisé sur les réseaux sociaux</h2><div class="source">Wired</div> <time datetime="17/12/2019 - 14:24" class="date">17/12/2019 - 14:24</time></div> </article></a> <a href="/revue-de-presse/terrorisme-la-turquie-nouvelle-base-arriere-des-djihadistes-de-daech"> <article class="item type-revuedepresse abo"><div class="item-image"><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" data-srcset="https://www.courrierinternational.com/sites/ci_master/files/styles/image_235/public/illustrations/thumbnails/turquie_9_0.jpg?itok=265G9HJz 380w, https://www.courrierinternational.com/sites/ci_master/files/styles/image_470/public/illustrations/thumbnails/turquie_9_0.jpg?itok=rzRvLxrL 1024w" data-src="https://www.courrierinternational.com/sites/ci_master/files/styles/image_235/public/illustrations/thumbnails/turquie_9_0.jpg?itok=265G9HJz" alt="La Turquie, nouvelle base arrière des djihadistes de Daech" sizes="(max-width:759px) 100vw, 50vw" class="lazyload"></div><div class="item-text"><h2 class="title"> <span class="strapline">Terrorisme.</span> La Turquie, nouvelle base arrière des djihadistes d